<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="container hero-container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        훼미리는 <span class="highlight">가족</span>입니다
      </h1>
      <h2 class="hero-subtitle">
        사랑과 신뢰가 있는 기업
      </h2>
      <p class="hero-description">
        훼미리식품은 엄선된 재료로 우리 가족이 먹는다는 생각으로 만들겠습니다. 
        과자류, 빙과류, 낙농품 등 다양한 식품을 통해 고객 여러분에게 
        행복과 즐거움을 전하기 위해 노력하고 있습니다.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#products" class="btn-primary">제품 살펴보기</a>
        <a href="#company" class="btn-secondary">회사 소개</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-image-container">
      <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
        <img 
          src="/images/hero-cookie.jpg" 
          alt="훼미리식품 제품 이미지" 
          class="hero-image"
        />
        <div class="hero-quote">
          <p>
            "행복하고 건강하게 그리고 맛있게 즐겨보는 세상살이 기분"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, white, #fff5eb);
  }
  
  .hero-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    order: 2;
  }
  
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .hero-title .highlight {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 5rem;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  
  .hero-description {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  
  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .hero-buttons a {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    border-radius: 60px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .hero-image-container {
    order: 1;
  }
  
  .hero-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .hero-quote {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .hero-quote p {
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .hero-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .hero-content {
      order: 1;
    }
    
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 10rem;
    }
    
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 6rem;
    }
    
    .hero-description {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
    
    .hero-image-container {
      order: 2;
    }
    
    .hero-image {
      height: 600px;
    }
    
    .hero-buttons a {
      font-size: 3rem;
      padding: 1.8rem 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
